        "id": "spatial_exhibition_world",
        "name": "Spatial Exhibition World",
        "confidence": 0.89,
        "reason": "The poster becomes strongest as a layered atmospheric chamber with shallow depth, orbiting labels, and slow camera travel.",
        "refs": [
